lead_paragraph: Two-time world champion James Magnussen is a late addition to the Australian swim team for the Olympics in Rio de Janeiro, securing a relay spot almost two months after missing individual selection for the 100-meter freestyle.

headline.print_headline: Magnussen Added to Australia's Swim Team for Olympics in Rio
